---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import SimpleCard from '../../components/cards/SimpleCard.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Research" description="Explore the DRAGGON Lab research vision.">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-950">Research</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-lg leading-8 text-slate-600">DRAGGON Lab builds AI-aided biodesign platforms across biological software foundations, DBTL workflows, machine learning, digital twins, and intelligent genetic networks.</p>
    <div class="mt-8 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-3">
      <SimpleCard title="Biological Software Foundations">Reusable software, standards, data structures, and metadata for programmable biology.</SimpleCard>
      <SimpleCard title="Automated DBTL Workflows">Programmatic workflows for genetic network engineering.</SimpleCard>
      <SimpleCard title="AI-Aided Biodesign">Models and data infrastructure for more predictable biological design.</SimpleCard>
      <SimpleCard title="Digital Twins of Living Systems">Simulations connecting engineered systems with cells and communities.</SimpleCard>
      <SimpleCard title="Intelligent Genetic & Genomic Networks">Biological architectures for sensing, computing, and decision-making.</SimpleCard>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
